sc%3DDESC&amp;tr_h=1345751318684351ef8c4d14_86993006"/><published>2025-06-06T22:22:36+08:00</published></entry><entry><id>76f7516d4802d889e9092940cb308955</id><title>想帶70歲阿媽上深圳鑲假牙，有冇啱長者睇嘅牙科推介？</title><updated>2025-06-03T12:09:44+08:00</updated><author><name>Bellomi</name></author><content type="html">&lt;p&gt;Published on: 2025-06-03T12:09:44+0800&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;div class="postmessage-content t_msgfont" id="postmessage_572679206"&gt;&lt;!-- google_ad_section_start --&gt;&lt;span id="postorig_572679206"&gt;想帶70歲阿媽上深圳鑲假牙，但佢驚牙醫講普通話溝通唔到，有冇啱長者睇嘅牙科推介？&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt; &lt;!-- google_ad_section_end --&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content><link href="https://www.discuss.com.hk/viewthread.php?tid=31945875&amp;utm_source=festival_fid&amp;utm_medium=110&amp;utm_campaign=841&amp;extra=page%3D1%26amp%3Bfilter%3D0%26amp%3Borderby%3Ddateline%26amp%3Bascdesc%3DDESC"/><published>2025-06-03T12:09:44+08:00</published></entry></feed>